<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Walther von Seckendorff zu Stopfenheim</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Fürsprache bei Burggraf Friedrich VI. von Nürnberg wegen des Geleits für Nürnberger Kaufleute zu und von der Nördlinger Messe.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_113" id="56r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_113_r3l3"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> VValther von Seckendorff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l4">cʒu Stoppfenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><note place="topright">
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l1"><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> von geleits vvegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l2">in die meſſe gen <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></note>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l5"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her VValther / VVir biten <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hochvvirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan></del> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l6">daʒ Jr von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Burggraf fridrichs wegen ſchıcken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l7">vnd beſtellen wöllet / daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger kauffleute vnd auch Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l8">hab vnd kauffmanſchaft <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> in die meſſe gen <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd vvider </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l9">darauſʒ durch <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Burgraf <expan>fridr<ex>ichs</ex></expan> herſchaft vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l10">gepiete ſicher 
<del rend="strikethrough">t </del> geleẏtet werden / Als vvir ew des vvol getrawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l11">das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir vmb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allcʒeit gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l12">lat vns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gütlich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wıder <expan>vviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> beẏ dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l13"><expan>gegenvvertige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>feſt<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Penthecoſt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r3l14">Anno <expan>deci<ex>m</ex>o</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_113" id="56r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Walther von Seckendorff czu Stoppfenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="topright">
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> von geleits wegen in die messe gen
                                        <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex>.</expan>
</note>
</app>
<expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Walther, wir biten
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz,
                        daz ir von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, burggraf Fridrichs, wegen schicken und
                        bestellen wöllet, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, kauffleute und
                        auch ir hab und kauffmanschaft <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> in die
                        messe gen <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan> und wider darausz durch
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, burgraf <expan>Fridr<ex>ichs</ex></expan>,
                        herschaft und gepiete sicher geleytet werden, als wir ew des wol getrawen.
                        Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allczeit gern
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> und lat uns des
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gütlich,
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> bey dem
                                <expan>gegenwertige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>fest<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>penthecost<ex>en</ex></expan> anno <expan>deci<ex>m</ex>o</expan>. </ab></div>
</div></body>
